Press Files Series is divided into the following subseries: Clippings; Videos;
                  Floor Statements; Speeches; Press Issues; Press Releases; TV and Radio Files;
                  Newsletters; Editorials; Special Mailings; and Photographs.

The Personal/Political series is divided into the following subseries: General
                  Correspondence; Personal Correspondence; Correspondence Subject Files; Budget;
                  Campaign; Appointment Books; Memoranda; Nominations; Advisory Board; Invitations;
                  and Personal Journals.
